WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:01:35.400

00:01:40.105 --> 00:01:41.785
FAIR AND JUST, LOYAL AND TRUE

00:02:01.265 --> 00:02:02.625
YUXI CIGARETTE

00:02:07.985 --> 00:02:09.744
Stop looking.

00:02:10.625 --> 00:02:12.025
He is not coming.

00:02:12.105 --> 00:02:13.945
You should just come with me
to the cement factory.

00:02:14.025 --> 00:02:15.505
Let's wait a bit longer.

00:02:15.585 --> 00:02:17.225
He told the property management
on the phone

00:02:17.305 --> 00:02:18.145
that he would come in person.

00:02:19.985 --> 00:02:23.145
Trying to deal with someone like
Song Qingsong, you are still too green.

00:02:23.665 --> 00:02:25.785
Just this bag of stuff.

00:02:25.865 --> 00:02:27.545
It means nothing to him.

00:02:28.145 --> 00:02:31.105
-Why would he come?
-What if he feels guilty?

00:02:31.185 --> 00:02:33.345
What if there's something at home
he doesn't want anyone

00:02:33.425 --> 00:02:34.665
or the police to find?

00:02:35.305 --> 00:02:36.705
I think the one feeling guilty is you.

00:02:41.465 --> 00:02:44.265
Keep staring, and you will turn
into Meng Jiangnv.

00:02:47.505 --> 00:02:53.665
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY, WEIYANG CITY

00:03:05.625 --> 00:03:06.465
What are you doing?

00:03:07.105 --> 00:03:09.545
That guy dared to harm Wolf.
I am going to cripple him.

00:03:09.625 --> 00:03:11.505
Do you even have a brain?

00:03:11.585 --> 00:03:13.105
Did you forget we have transformed?

00:03:13.185 --> 00:03:15.385
Still talking about knives and guns?
Put it away.

00:03:15.465 --> 00:03:18.065
Mr. Jin, you said it yourself,
we were going to deal with him.

00:03:18.145 --> 00:03:21.865
Do you know who owns that car
with plate 688?

00:03:21.945 --> 00:03:24.225
The boss of Qingsong Cement Factory,

00:03:24.305 --> 00:03:25.745
Song Qingsong.

00:03:26.505 --> 00:03:28.265
How many lives do you think
you have to mess with him?

00:03:28.865 --> 00:03:30.425
So we are not avenging Wolf?

00:03:30.945 --> 00:03:33.385
We need to figure out the situation first
before we take revenge.

00:03:33.985 --> 00:03:36.945
How did Song Qingsong
get involved with Manlang?

00:03:37.025 --> 00:03:38.225
Alright.

00:03:38.745 --> 00:03:40.185
That makes sense.

00:03:50.385 --> 00:03:51.625
Follow him.

00:03:55.505 --> 00:03:57.305
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY, WEIYANG CITY

00:04:16.944 --> 00:04:19.624
If any words Song Qingsong said were true,

00:04:20.345 --> 00:04:23.985
every pig in Weiyang
would be climbing trees.

00:05:16.545 --> 00:05:17.785
Criminal Department.

00:05:17.865 --> 00:05:19.185
A Mercedes just arrived at the entrance.

00:05:19.265 --> 00:05:20.705
They say they are
the owner from Yuanlongli.

00:05:23.305 --> 00:05:24.825
Let them in.

00:05:25.585 --> 00:05:27.505
-Brigade meeting room.
-Got it.

00:05:34.385 --> 00:05:36.585
Come on. We'll be seeing pigs climb trees.

00:05:41.465 --> 00:05:43.145
Hey.

00:05:43.825 --> 00:05:45.225
Why the rush?

00:05:45.305 --> 00:05:47.665
Have you figured out
how to question him about Xu Meng?

00:05:47.745 --> 00:05:49.345
Go through every detail
and verify everything.

00:05:49.425 --> 00:05:52.105
As long as there are inconsistencies,
we will find a breakthrough.

00:05:53.185 --> 00:05:56.225
Song Qingsong
is the victim, not a suspect.

00:05:56.305 --> 00:05:58.945
What if he just takes his stuff
and leaves without saying anything?

00:05:59.025 --> 00:06:00.825
Tell me, what will you do then?

00:06:07.345 --> 00:06:08.425
So what is your plan?

00:06:17.545 --> 00:06:19.185
Very simple. Five words.

00:06:20.145 --> 00:06:21.585
We will work in tandem.

00:06:23.905 --> 00:06:24.945
How?

00:06:26.145 --> 00:06:27.105
I lead, you back me up.

00:06:27.705 --> 00:06:29.185
I ease him in, you pin him down.

00:06:29.265 --> 00:06:31.265
I play the good cop, you play the bad cop.

00:06:31.345 --> 00:06:32.185
Got it?

00:06:33.705 --> 00:06:35.785
Are you sure
that's really your real intention?

00:06:37.745 --> 00:06:39.385
Just tell me. Do you get it or not?

00:06:43.105 --> 00:06:44.265
SPECIAL TASK FORCE

00:06:44.345 --> 00:06:45.185
The good cop goes first.

00:06:53.865 --> 00:06:57.585
What is Song Qingsong
doing at the police station?

00:06:58.465 --> 00:07:00.745
Could the police have traced
the Wolf case back to him?

00:07:00.825 --> 00:07:02.385
Trace, my foot.

00:07:02.465 --> 00:07:03.905
If they had, he'd be here in a police car.

00:07:03.985 --> 00:07:04.985
Right.

00:07:07.345 --> 00:07:08.625
You just reminded me.

00:07:09.225 --> 00:07:12.185
If Song Qingsong
really had dealings with Manlang,

00:07:12.705 --> 00:07:15.065
-then we could…
-We can squeeze him for a big payout.

00:07:15.145 --> 00:07:16.305
Squeeze your head.

00:07:16.385 --> 00:07:18.985
Jeez. We need to think differently.

00:07:19.065 --> 00:07:22.705
Use this opportunity
to talk to Song Qingsong.

00:07:22.785 --> 00:07:24.825
Get him to throw us some business.

00:07:25.425 --> 00:07:29.305
That's called "Water flows downhill,
people move up."

00:07:29.385 --> 00:07:30.905
Move up?

00:07:30.985 --> 00:07:33.705
What Song Qingsong did before
was way worse than what we did.

00:07:33.785 --> 00:07:34.705
I…

00:07:35.425 --> 00:07:37.265
If someone like him can clean up his act,

00:07:37.345 --> 00:07:40.905
then I should learn from him.

00:07:51.945 --> 00:07:53.625
ID and letter of introduction are fine.

00:07:58.385 --> 00:07:59.785
This tea tastes terrible.

00:08:02.705 --> 00:08:03.865
Wait.

00:08:03.945 --> 00:08:05.985
The owner has to come in person
to claim the stolen items.

00:08:06.065 --> 00:08:07.265
Call Song Qingsong.

00:08:07.345 --> 00:08:08.745
Have him come himself.

00:08:09.265 --> 00:08:12.145
Officer,
I have already made it very clear.

00:08:12.225 --> 00:08:15.745
The house belongs to my brother-in-law,
but I have been living there recently.

00:08:15.825 --> 00:08:18.505
So everything in the safe belongs to me.

00:08:20.025 --> 00:08:22.585
Alright. Let's verify everything,
one by one.

00:08:23.305 --> 00:08:24.265
What do you mean?

00:08:24.345 --> 00:08:25.865
Where were you earlier?

00:08:26.425 --> 00:08:29.465
By procedure, we need to confirm
in person that the items are yours

00:08:30.065 --> 00:08:31.145
before you can take them.

00:08:35.144 --> 00:08:36.185
Please go ahead.

00:08:42.264 --> 00:08:44.225
What brand is the liquor?
How many bottles?

00:08:44.825 --> 00:08:47.145
Moutai. 53-degree Feitian.

00:08:47.225 --> 00:08:48.225
-Four bottles.
-Cigarettes?

00:08:48.305 --> 00:08:49.345
Zhonghua. Four cartons.

00:08:50.065 --> 00:08:51.185
Four cartons of Zhonghua.

00:08:54.185 --> 00:08:55.985
-Yuxi.
-Two cartons.

00:08:58.305 --> 00:08:59.665
Two cartons of Yuxi.

00:08:59.745 --> 00:09:01.065
Flip-top Yuxi.

00:09:05.345 --> 00:09:06.505
Belts?

00:09:06.585 --> 00:09:08.425
Two belts.

00:09:08.505 --> 00:09:10.145
One gold Rolex.

00:09:10.225 --> 00:09:11.785
Three gold rings.

00:09:11.865 --> 00:09:13.225
Five gold chains.

00:09:13.305 --> 00:09:14.585
Two lighters.

00:09:14.665 --> 00:09:15.905
Three bundles of cash.

00:09:15.985 --> 00:09:17.145
Bring everything out.

00:09:17.745 --> 00:09:19.345
How much cash?

00:09:22.425 --> 00:09:25.865
Hundred-yuan bills.
Three bundles. Ten thousand each.

00:09:26.665 --> 00:09:28.185
That makes 30,000.

00:09:33.705 --> 00:09:34.545
He.

00:09:35.065 --> 00:09:37.425
That number sounds familiar.

00:09:38.425 --> 00:09:39.545
Yeah, it does.

00:09:39.625 --> 00:09:41.345
I heard there's a rule on the street.

00:09:41.425 --> 00:09:45.425
Say it's a 40,000-yuan job,
you pay 10,000 upfront,

00:09:45.505 --> 00:09:48.585
then the remaining 30 after it's done.

00:09:48.665 --> 00:09:50.345
And there's usually a little bonus, right?

00:09:51.105 --> 00:09:52.745
At least

00:09:53.385 --> 00:09:55.425
two cartons of flip-top Yuxi.

00:10:03.825 --> 00:10:04.665
Keep going.

00:10:05.385 --> 00:10:06.665
I don't have all day.

00:10:06.745 --> 00:10:08.185
Have you checked everything?

00:10:08.265 --> 00:10:09.145
Can I go now?

00:10:12.825 --> 00:10:13.865
Darn it.

00:10:28.305 --> 00:10:30.185
My watch… Where is my gold Rolex?
Where is the money?

00:10:30.265 --> 00:10:32.105
-Where is my briefcase?
-What briefcase?

00:10:35.025 --> 00:10:36.545
Briefcase… There is no briefcase.

00:10:36.625 --> 00:10:37.785
You remembered it wrong.

00:10:37.865 --> 00:10:38.945
I am a bit confused.

00:10:39.665 --> 00:10:41.305
I have been here too long.

00:10:47.305 --> 00:10:49.505
You mean Song Qingsong's briefcase?

00:10:49.585 --> 00:10:50.945
No, no. I remembered it wrong.
There wasn't one.

00:10:51.025 --> 00:10:54.145
It had "Qingsong Cement"
written on it, right?

00:10:54.225 --> 00:10:55.265
I remembered it wrong.

00:10:55.345 --> 00:10:56.425
Something in that bag you don't want seen?

00:10:56.505 --> 00:11:00.145
Call Song Qingsong.
Tell him the briefcase is missing.

00:11:04.945 --> 00:11:06.545
Take the items.

00:11:06.625 --> 00:11:07.825
Get to Dahuihuang now.

00:11:10.145 --> 00:11:12.745
I still have work.
Is it done now? Can I leave?

00:11:12.825 --> 00:11:16.265
Are you sure that's everything?
Nothing else? A watch?

00:11:16.345 --> 00:11:17.825
-Cash?
-I am sure.

00:11:18.745 --> 00:11:20.105
That is all.

00:11:41.705 --> 00:11:42.865
"Build strength."

00:11:43.465 --> 00:11:44.785
What is that?

00:11:45.385 --> 00:11:47.065
"Forge the police…"

00:11:47.145 --> 00:11:48.425
What is that?

00:11:50.065 --> 00:11:53.985
"Build strength, forge the police soul."

00:11:57.905 --> 00:11:59.145
You don't recognize the "soul" character?

00:11:59.225 --> 00:12:00.825
What does it mean?

00:12:00.905 --> 00:12:03.665
Those two characters look a bit creepy.

00:12:05.785 --> 00:12:07.505
It has two meanings.

00:12:08.025 --> 00:12:11.905
One is ghost, the other is spirit.

00:12:11.985 --> 00:12:13.465
-Got it?
-Got it.

00:12:13.545 --> 00:12:15.145
I have plenty of spirit.

00:12:16.585 --> 00:12:17.785
Whose kid are you?

00:12:17.865 --> 00:12:20.265
My dad is He Yuanhang.

00:12:21.105 --> 00:12:23.385
That Officer He on secondment.
I have heard of him.

00:12:23.465 --> 00:12:25.385
Miss, I need to use the restroom.

00:12:25.465 --> 00:12:26.825
Do you know where it is?

00:12:26.905 --> 00:12:28.625
Yes. I will take you.

00:12:30.425 --> 00:12:31.345
Let's go.

00:12:35.505 --> 00:12:36.465
Xiaohe.

00:12:37.505 --> 00:12:39.705
Your shoelace is undone. Let me tie it.

00:12:46.025 --> 00:12:47.105
Miss, he is looking at your waist.

00:12:48.825 --> 00:12:50.665
-Don't go. You're a bad guy.
-Hey.

00:12:50.745 --> 00:12:52.345
Kid, you're mistaken.

00:12:52.425 --> 00:12:56.025
-Mistaken? Kids don't lie.
-Dad, there's a pervert here!

00:12:56.105 --> 00:12:58.065
-What have you done?
-What is going on?

00:13:01.265 --> 00:13:03.545
Let go. Is this your child?

00:13:03.625 --> 00:13:05.705
None of your business.
Sharp face. Dark circles.

00:13:05.785 --> 00:13:08.305
You look kind of creepy.

00:13:08.385 --> 00:13:09.505
Like a pervert.

00:13:11.065 --> 00:13:14.145
At such a young age,
your temper is already this bad.

00:13:14.225 --> 00:13:15.945
You'd better watch yourself
when you grow up.

00:13:16.545 --> 00:13:18.185
-Hey!
-I am just telling the truth.

00:13:18.265 --> 00:13:19.985
You do need to be careful out there.

00:13:26.385 --> 00:13:27.625
He,

00:13:28.145 --> 00:13:30.745
when we mentioned the briefcase,
his eyes went right.

00:13:30.825 --> 00:13:32.905
When we mentioned the cash,
they shifted left.

00:13:33.585 --> 00:13:36.025
He was lying about the briefcase,

00:13:36.105 --> 00:13:38.265
but the 30,000 in cash,
he was recalling it.

00:13:40.305 --> 00:13:42.425
The one who hired someone
is very likely him.

00:13:44.025 --> 00:13:46.625
He should be on his way now
to find Song Qingsong.

00:13:47.265 --> 00:13:48.705
Song Qingsong.

00:13:49.825 --> 00:13:50.945
Officer He,

00:13:51.465 --> 00:13:54.385
if you're going out, leave Xiaohe with me.

00:13:54.465 --> 00:13:55.945
I'm Liang Juan from the Analysis Unit.

00:13:56.025 --> 00:13:58.585
I'm on the night shift. I can take her
to the cafeteria later.

00:14:05.385 --> 00:14:07.025
Thank you, Officer Liang.

00:14:07.105 --> 00:14:08.385
-Not at all.
-Kiddo,

00:14:08.465 --> 00:14:09.945
I'll come back to pick you up later.

00:14:10.025 --> 00:14:11.985
-Listen to Ms. Liang, alright?
-Okay.

00:14:13.985 --> 00:14:17.145
So you are the new top graduate
in the Criminal Department.

00:14:17.985 --> 00:14:19.025
He is.

00:14:19.905 --> 00:14:20.945
Hello.

00:14:21.025 --> 00:14:22.985
You two work well together.

00:14:23.785 --> 00:14:24.785
Right, Xiaohe?

00:14:27.185 --> 00:14:28.265
Let's go.

00:14:29.625 --> 00:14:30.785
He's out.

00:14:33.985 --> 00:14:34.905
Wait.

00:14:36.665 --> 00:14:37.905
He Yuanhang.

00:14:39.225 --> 00:14:41.705
The cops are following him.
Should we still follow?

00:14:42.425 --> 00:14:43.465
Yes.

00:15:13.225 --> 00:15:18.585
He, just the Yuxi cigarettes
and Wu Shanlong's reactions aren't enough.

00:15:18.665 --> 00:15:20.825
Even if we follow him
and find Song Qingsong,

00:15:21.425 --> 00:15:22.625
we need a plan first.

00:15:22.705 --> 00:15:24.385
What plan?

00:15:24.465 --> 00:15:25.825
Get him back to the station first,
no matter what.

00:15:27.585 --> 00:15:31.225
What? Even a top graduate like you
consults me now?

00:15:34.425 --> 00:15:38.385
I have noticed your methods
can be quite effective at times.

00:15:39.105 --> 00:15:40.545
There are only three days left.

00:15:40.625 --> 00:15:41.985
If we don't use some tactics,
we won't get anywhere.

00:15:42.065 --> 00:15:44.065
This missing persons case looks simple,

00:15:44.585 --> 00:15:45.785
but the deeper we dig,
the more complicated it gets.

00:15:45.865 --> 00:15:47.385
It is like a maze.

00:15:48.425 --> 00:15:49.465
A maze?

00:15:50.745 --> 00:15:54.425
I do have a theory for that.
Trémaux's algorithm.

00:15:54.505 --> 00:15:56.705
Don't even start. My head is spinning.

00:16:12.785 --> 00:16:14.105
Is it funny?

00:16:21.105 --> 00:16:23.425
Come on. You sing. Go on. Just sing.

00:16:23.505 --> 00:16:24.585
‎Come on, sing it!

00:16:25.105 --> 00:16:26.225
Sing.

00:16:33.025 --> 00:16:35.585
-Director Li.
-Song Qingsong.

00:16:35.665 --> 00:16:37.065
What's your order?

00:16:37.905 --> 00:16:39.025
Where are you?

00:16:39.545 --> 00:16:41.585
-At the factory.
-At the factory?

00:16:42.425 --> 00:16:43.985
Do you know about the mine break-in?

00:16:44.065 --> 00:16:44.905
No.

00:16:48.625 --> 00:16:51.065
Well, I just got back
from a business trip.

00:16:54.545 --> 00:16:56.065
Are the documents still there?

00:16:56.145 --> 00:16:58.265
Still there? They have all been taken.

00:16:58.345 --> 00:16:59.945
The police are involved now.

00:17:00.025 --> 00:17:02.065
I've been told to issue a statement
declaring all the stolen documents

00:17:02.145 --> 00:17:03.225
null and void.

00:17:03.305 --> 00:17:04.424
Yours too.

00:17:05.145 --> 00:17:08.184
Director Li, the documents may be voided,

00:17:08.704 --> 00:17:10.825
but my money isn't, right?

00:17:10.905 --> 00:17:12.545
Are you out of your mind?

00:17:12.625 --> 00:17:13.865
Talking about this on the phone?

00:17:14.905 --> 00:17:16.985
Was the mine really robbed?

00:17:17.505 --> 00:17:18.865
-Or was it…
-Enough.

00:17:18.944 --> 00:17:22.105
Cut the crap. Burn the documents now.

00:17:22.184 --> 00:17:24.545
If anyone sees them, it's on you.

00:17:25.065 --> 00:17:26.224
Do you hear me?

00:17:27.145 --> 00:17:27.985
Hello?

00:17:28.065 --> 00:17:29.385
-Again.
-Song Qingsong.

00:17:30.065 --> 00:17:31.185
-Another one.
-Do you hear me?

00:17:31.265 --> 00:17:32.705
Trying to set me up.

00:17:40.025 --> 00:17:42.345
Mr. Liu, where are you now?

00:17:43.185 --> 00:17:44.825
Here's the situation.

00:17:45.345 --> 00:17:47.465
Something just came up on my end.

00:17:47.545 --> 00:17:50.425
My driver lost the documents.

00:17:50.505 --> 00:17:53.705
When you arrive, we'll talk…

00:17:54.625 --> 00:17:55.825
Liu?

00:17:56.545 --> 00:17:57.545
Hello?

00:17:58.665 --> 00:17:59.905
Hello?

00:18:09.025 --> 00:18:15.425
DAHUIHUANG NIGHTCLUB

00:18:39.425 --> 00:18:40.865
That fool Song Qingsong is not in the car.

00:18:41.705 --> 00:18:43.745
Then who is this idiot?

00:18:52.065 --> 00:18:53.985
Welcome, boss.
We are glad to have you here.

00:18:54.065 --> 00:18:56.185
Wasn't it plate 688?

00:18:56.265 --> 00:18:57.825
You sure?

00:18:57.905 --> 00:18:59.145
I'm sure.

00:19:03.705 --> 00:19:07.465
Mr. Jin, I know someone
who'll remember it better than me.

00:19:15.545 --> 00:19:16.545
He.

00:19:17.265 --> 00:19:19.545
-He.
-What?

00:19:21.185 --> 00:19:23.225
We are just walking in like this?

00:19:24.145 --> 00:19:26.105
If not, are we supposed to climb in?

00:19:28.025 --> 00:19:29.625
You've done raids here before, have you?

00:19:29.705 --> 00:19:32.625
Even if I have, it doesn't stop you
from investigating.

00:19:38.385 --> 00:19:39.265
What I mean is,

00:19:39.345 --> 00:19:41.905
should we

00:19:43.345 --> 00:19:44.905
coordinate a bit?

00:19:48.145 --> 00:19:49.865
You lead, I back you up.

00:19:49.945 --> 00:19:51.905
You play one role, I play the other.

00:19:51.985 --> 00:19:52.865
That one.

00:19:54.305 --> 00:19:56.385
This time, you're the one asking me.

00:19:58.425 --> 00:20:00.625
What do you mean by "asking"?

00:20:01.305 --> 00:20:02.385
We're partners.

00:20:02.465 --> 00:20:03.905
Exactly.

00:20:03.985 --> 00:20:07.065
On a case, you have to lower yourself
and act naturally.

00:20:07.145 --> 00:20:08.425
Let's go.

00:20:13.745 --> 00:20:16.425
Welcome, boss.
We are glad to have you here.

00:20:17.025 --> 00:20:19.025
Police. Get Ms. Xia over.

00:20:19.105 --> 00:20:20.265
Alright.

00:20:32.065 --> 00:20:33.745
Mr. Song, I brought it.

00:20:35.345 --> 00:20:36.465
Now?

00:20:36.545 --> 00:20:39.105
What's the point now?

00:20:39.185 --> 00:20:40.585
No, but…

00:20:40.665 --> 00:20:41.585
I brought it.

00:20:42.465 --> 00:20:46.025
Eight million, and I ended up
with a pile of scrap! Scrap!

00:20:46.865 --> 00:20:49.665
Li, you are dead.

00:20:51.465 --> 00:20:52.625
Officer He.

00:20:53.665 --> 00:20:55.585
Officer He, what brings you here today?

00:20:55.665 --> 00:20:56.545
Checking up on us?

00:20:56.625 --> 00:20:59.625
Don't worry.
We're running things legally now.

00:20:59.705 --> 00:21:00.865
We won't break the rules.

00:21:00.945 --> 00:21:04.025
You said that last time.
And the time before.

00:21:04.865 --> 00:21:06.225
We have been making improvements.

00:21:08.345 --> 00:21:10.305
Let me ask you,
which room is Song Qingsong in?

00:21:10.985 --> 00:21:13.345
What Song Qingsong?

00:21:13.425 --> 00:21:14.705
Never heard of him.

00:21:15.985 --> 00:21:17.225
What about Wu Shanlong?

00:21:17.305 --> 00:21:18.425
Which room is Wu Shanlong in?

00:21:19.145 --> 00:21:22.585
Officer He, I don't know who they are.

00:21:22.665 --> 00:21:24.425
I've never heard of their names.

00:21:26.225 --> 00:21:28.385
Ran, make a call.
Get the Public Order Unit over here.

00:21:30.505 --> 00:21:35.385
Okay. Maybe we should also call
the fire, commerce, and tax too.

00:21:35.465 --> 00:21:37.065
-We should call them all.
-Good idea. Call them all.

00:21:37.145 --> 00:21:39.585
-Alright.
-No need.

00:21:39.665 --> 00:21:42.745
There's no need to make a fuss over this.
Everyone is tired, right?

00:21:44.145 --> 00:21:45.385
Oh my goodness.

00:21:48.225 --> 00:21:49.545
What are you still doing here?

00:21:50.265 --> 00:21:51.625
Get lost!

00:21:54.305 --> 00:21:57.385
Mr. Song, getting angry
is bad for your health.

00:21:57.465 --> 00:21:58.825
Who the heck are you?

00:22:00.065 --> 00:22:01.985
Mr. Song, they're police.

00:22:05.665 --> 00:22:07.785
I'm He Yuanhang from the Nanshan Branch.

00:22:08.585 --> 00:22:11.145
I just got off work.
So I brought a colleague out to relax.

00:22:11.225 --> 00:22:14.185
We heard you were here,
so we came by to pay a visit.

00:22:14.265 --> 00:22:16.465
I cannot stand the cops. Get out.

00:22:16.545 --> 00:22:18.745
Song Qingsong, we have received a report

00:22:18.825 --> 00:22:21.145
that you solicited prostitution
at Dahuihuang.

00:22:23.825 --> 00:22:25.585
Who is making
false accusations against me?

00:22:26.225 --> 00:22:28.225
This briefcase contains
the payment, does it not?

00:22:33.145 --> 00:22:34.665
The things inside the briefcase
are important documents

00:22:34.745 --> 00:22:36.785
from the cement factory.
They're confidential.

00:22:36.865 --> 00:22:39.425
Without a warrant,
no one is allowed to touch it.

00:22:39.505 --> 00:22:41.145
I will call my superiors right now.

00:22:42.065 --> 00:22:43.145
It is a misunderstanding.

00:22:43.705 --> 00:22:44.745
It must be.

00:22:45.345 --> 00:22:47.225
How could Mr. Song
possibly do such a thing?

00:22:47.305 --> 00:22:50.385
Right, I almost forgot.

00:22:50.465 --> 00:22:52.345
I have something here
for you to take a look at.

00:22:52.425 --> 00:22:54.185
Do you know this woman?

00:22:54.785 --> 00:22:55.705
I do not.

00:22:55.785 --> 00:22:57.385
Let me remind you.

00:22:57.465 --> 00:22:59.225
Muse Foot Massage. Mengmeng.

00:22:59.945 --> 00:23:01.825
Just last week, you hit her.

00:23:01.905 --> 00:23:03.105
Nonsense.

00:23:03.625 --> 00:23:04.905
I never hit women.

00:23:05.585 --> 00:23:06.425
Do you have any evidence?

00:23:07.025 --> 00:23:07.985
If you have none, get lost.

00:23:11.065 --> 00:23:12.425
Mr. Wu,

00:23:13.625 --> 00:23:14.905
we didn't get a chance to thank you.

00:23:14.985 --> 00:23:18.025
If you hadn't led the way,
how would we have met Mr. Song?

00:23:19.505 --> 00:23:21.305
Mr. Song, they came on their own.

00:23:21.385 --> 00:23:23.785
You went to the station yourself
to claim the lost items, right?

00:23:23.865 --> 00:23:26.705
You said your brother-in-law,
Mr. Song, has treated you well,

00:23:26.785 --> 00:23:28.785
so why are you still raking in so much?

00:23:28.865 --> 00:23:33.345
Moutai, Zhonghua, a gold Rolex,
and gold chains.

00:23:33.425 --> 00:23:34.465
That's over a hundred thousand.

00:23:34.545 --> 00:23:36.665
Nonsense. You're slandering me!

00:23:36.745 --> 00:23:39.745
Mr. Wu,
you have been very cooperative today.

00:23:39.825 --> 00:23:42.385
You told the Criminal Department
a lot about Mr. Song,

00:23:43.065 --> 00:23:44.425
especially about that briefcase.

00:23:44.505 --> 00:23:46.665
We had no idea it meant so much to him.

00:23:46.745 --> 00:23:48.505
Even when Mengmeng merely touched it,

00:23:48.585 --> 00:23:50.625
he made sure she disappeared from Weiyang.

00:23:50.705 --> 00:23:52.025
You're framing me! Nonsense!

00:23:52.625 --> 00:23:53.905
Bastard!

00:23:53.985 --> 00:23:55.345
-You bastard!
-You let go!

00:23:55.425 --> 00:23:56.465
Qingsong!

00:23:56.545 --> 00:23:58.625
-If he goes too far, arrest him.
-They are…

00:23:58.705 --> 00:24:01.185
They are clearly trying to drive
a wedge between us.

00:24:05.105 --> 00:24:06.305
Assaulting police officers is a crime.

00:24:11.025 --> 00:24:12.825
The police are hitting me!

00:24:18.545 --> 00:24:20.745
-Qingsong, run!
-Stop right there.

00:24:20.825 --> 00:24:22.425
-Let go.
-Qingsong, run!

00:24:22.505 --> 00:24:23.625
-Stop.
-Qingsong.

00:24:23.705 --> 00:24:24.625
Vice squad!

00:24:26.345 --> 00:24:28.185
Vice squad!

00:24:28.265 --> 00:24:31.745
Vice squad!

00:24:32.465 --> 00:24:34.785
-Run!
-Vice raid! Run!

00:24:39.825 --> 00:24:40.865
‎Hurry! Run!

00:24:42.665 --> 00:24:43.705
Is that him? Right?

00:24:43.785 --> 00:24:45.465
-No. Not him.
-Is that him?

00:24:48.705 --> 00:24:49.825
This way.

00:24:51.665 --> 00:24:52.745
Leave now!

00:25:04.185 --> 00:25:05.185
Mr. Jin.

00:25:05.265 --> 00:25:06.705
The one who climbed down the pipe.

00:25:06.785 --> 00:25:08.745
That is him! That is him!

00:25:11.305 --> 00:25:13.745
You still recognize him
with that injury on his head?

00:25:13.825 --> 00:25:15.825
Mr. Jin, I never forget a face.

00:25:15.905 --> 00:25:17.945
-Bring him here. Hurry.
-Alright.

00:25:19.385 --> 00:25:20.785
DAHUIHUANG NIGHTCLUB

00:25:25.025 --> 00:25:26.505
-He, drive.
-Mr. Jin.

00:25:27.185 --> 00:25:28.185
Police.

00:25:31.145 --> 00:25:32.505
Fuck.

00:25:32.585 --> 00:25:34.065
One after another.

00:25:34.585 --> 00:25:35.665
What is this, Snake?

00:25:38.865 --> 00:25:40.185
Behind us.

00:25:55.905 --> 00:25:56.985
Son of a bitch!

00:26:14.385 --> 00:26:15.345
Faster. Go faster.

00:26:15.425 --> 00:26:17.265
This is just a Fukang.
He's driving a Benz.

00:26:17.345 --> 00:26:19.705
If Song Qingsong gets away this time,
it will be hard to find him again.

00:26:42.145 --> 00:26:45.025
Song Qingsong,
I will not let you get away.

00:26:45.105 --> 00:26:47.105
He, don't lose your head. Be careful.

00:26:47.185 --> 00:26:49.825
At this point, whoever eases off loses.

00:26:49.905 --> 00:26:52.385
He's cutting me off.
Then I'll cut him off too.

00:26:52.465 --> 00:26:55.265
If there's an accident,
we'll bring both him and the car in.

00:26:55.785 --> 00:26:56.705
That works.

00:26:58.985 --> 00:27:00.545
He, accelerate.

00:27:33.265 --> 00:27:35.865
Benz, here I come.

00:27:47.705 --> 00:27:48.985
Come on.

00:27:54.385 --> 00:27:55.545
It won't move?

00:27:56.185 --> 00:27:57.385
Hurry up.

00:27:57.465 --> 00:27:58.545
-I can't move it!
-They're gone.

00:28:11.585 --> 00:28:13.545
Song Qingsong, you scoundrel!

00:28:13.625 --> 00:28:15.825
You wrecked my car. I'm not done with you!

00:28:21.185 --> 00:28:24.625
Wu Shanlong,
didn't you say it was in the safe?

00:28:24.705 --> 00:28:27.145
What a coincidence
that the thief just happened to take it.

00:28:27.225 --> 00:28:29.625
Wu Shanlong, are you playing me?

00:28:29.705 --> 00:28:33.265
Stop yelling at me.

00:28:33.345 --> 00:28:35.145
Everyone has been yelling at me today.

00:28:36.145 --> 00:28:37.865
I'm telling you,
even if we got the documents,

00:28:37.945 --> 00:28:39.065
they're useless now.

00:28:39.145 --> 00:28:40.665
Useless?

00:28:40.745 --> 00:28:42.265
What do you mean? Explain.

00:28:42.785 --> 00:28:45.145
Dongshan Mine was robbed.
You know that, right?

00:28:45.225 --> 00:28:46.385
The bidding documents were inside.

00:28:46.465 --> 00:28:48.865
Song Qingsong is furious.

00:28:48.945 --> 00:28:50.905
He spent eight million
on a pile of worthless paper.

00:28:50.985 --> 00:28:54.425
You want to blackmail him
with that pile of worthless paper?

00:29:01.305 --> 00:29:02.305
The police came just now.

00:29:03.345 --> 00:29:07.105
They seem to be onto Mengmeng.

00:29:08.905 --> 00:29:10.865
If Song Qingsong gets arrested,

00:29:11.425 --> 00:29:12.785
neither of us is getting out of this.

00:29:14.425 --> 00:29:15.705
What do we do now?

00:29:17.105 --> 00:29:18.305
I know what to do.

00:29:21.945 --> 00:29:22.785
Hello?

00:29:24.225 --> 00:29:25.225
Hello?

00:29:55.745 --> 00:30:01.625
QINGSONG CEMENT

00:30:01.705 --> 00:30:08.705
FAIR AND JUST, LOYAL AND TRUE

00:30:13.185 --> 00:30:14.185
SPECIAL TASK FORCE MEMBER LIST

00:30:14.905 --> 00:30:16.865
-Xiaohe.
-Xiaohe.

00:30:16.945 --> 00:30:18.345
What major case is it this time?

00:30:18.425 --> 00:30:20.025
Four teenagers went missing
in Binchuan District.

00:30:20.105 --> 00:30:20.945
They still have not been found.

00:30:21.025 --> 00:30:22.785
Now the municipal bureau
is forming a special task force.

00:30:22.865 --> 00:30:24.025
Our district has to assist.

00:30:24.105 --> 00:30:25.185
Didn't they call you to join?

00:30:26.905 --> 00:30:28.425
Enough chatting. Meeting.

00:30:29.905 --> 00:30:31.065
We will go up first.

00:30:41.305 --> 00:30:43.065
Xiaohe, you're finally here.

00:30:43.145 --> 00:30:44.585
Captain Zhao has been looking for you.

00:30:44.665 --> 00:30:45.905
-For me?
-Go on.

00:30:47.785 --> 00:30:49.865
APPROVED

00:30:51.385 --> 00:30:54.225
-Captain Zhao.
-Come in.

00:30:54.305 --> 00:30:55.465
APPROVED BY ZHAO JIE

00:30:57.585 --> 00:30:58.705
Sit.

00:31:02.905 --> 00:31:04.025
Xiaohe,

00:31:04.785 --> 00:31:07.785
about Han Zi'ang's case,
I plan to assign it to you.

00:31:08.385 --> 00:31:09.425
Han Zi'ang's case?

00:31:10.625 --> 00:31:12.585
What about the one in Binchuan District?

00:31:15.025 --> 00:31:17.105
What, you think
this case isn't big enough?

00:31:18.585 --> 00:31:20.985
Of course not.
I wouldn't dare pick and choose.

00:31:21.065 --> 00:31:22.825
Captain, don't worry.

00:31:22.905 --> 00:31:24.665
I will make sure this case
is thoroughly investigated.

00:31:24.745 --> 00:31:27.785
About this case, Captain Qu
wrote a report yesterday.

00:31:28.305 --> 00:31:29.185
You can refer to it.

00:31:29.265 --> 00:31:30.185
Okay.

00:31:30.705 --> 00:31:32.865
From what we can tell,
it's most likely a prank.

00:31:32.945 --> 00:31:35.785
So, the focus is on cleanup
and calming the parents.

00:31:35.865 --> 00:31:37.025
Understood?

00:31:39.065 --> 00:31:41.185
CAPTAIN'S OFFICE

00:31:48.905 --> 00:31:50.145
One more thing.

00:31:50.905 --> 00:31:53.065
Sort out your family matters
as soon as possible.

00:32:04.905 --> 00:32:06.625
See? I told you.

00:32:07.145 --> 00:32:08.545
By seniority,

00:32:08.625 --> 00:32:11.345
Zhao Jie is still just a kid to me.

00:32:12.105 --> 00:32:15.025
He Yuanhang,
you should give up on that idea.

00:32:15.945 --> 00:32:16.985
I will not let you,

00:32:18.225 --> 00:32:20.345
or any of you, get involved in this case.

00:32:21.425 --> 00:32:24.225
Just treat me and Mr. Ran as helpers.

00:32:24.305 --> 00:32:26.465
No need to feed us. We won't steal credit.

00:32:26.545 --> 00:32:28.185
All upside.

00:32:28.265 --> 00:32:31.065
If you keep causing trouble,
I'll transfer back to the archives

00:32:31.145 --> 00:32:32.825
-and sit there doing nothing.
-No, no.

00:32:34.185 --> 00:32:36.065
I'm begging you. Please.

00:32:36.145 --> 00:32:38.705
Help Mr. Ran, okay?

00:32:38.785 --> 00:32:40.105
There is nothing I can do to help him.

00:32:40.185 --> 00:32:42.825
He Xiaohe, that is Mr. Ran.

00:32:42.905 --> 00:32:44.265
He watched you grow up.

00:32:44.345 --> 00:32:46.105
Have you forgotten how good he was to you?

00:32:46.185 --> 00:32:47.465
I have not.

00:32:48.305 --> 00:32:49.785
He's doing quite well now.

00:32:49.865 --> 00:32:51.865
Stop bothering him.
It's not good for either of you.

00:32:54.705 --> 00:32:56.625
He's just pretending he's fine.

00:32:57.265 --> 00:33:00.305
Since I came back, I have looked into it.

00:33:00.385 --> 00:33:03.305
I found that he's still avoiding
that case from back then.

00:33:03.905 --> 00:33:05.265
It's his demon.

00:33:05.905 --> 00:33:08.265
We need to help him face it.

00:33:08.345 --> 00:33:10.065
-Face it?
-Right.

00:33:10.145 --> 00:33:12.545
-And then?
-Then,

00:33:13.065 --> 00:33:16.505
he stays in Weiyang
and rejoins the Criminal Department.

00:33:16.585 --> 00:33:18.425
You're dreaming again.

00:33:18.505 --> 00:33:19.865
He's a university lecturer now.

00:33:19.945 --> 00:33:22.145
Can he just be transferred back
to the Criminal Department?

00:33:23.105 --> 00:33:24.945
Besides, he's doing great in Beijing.

00:33:25.025 --> 00:33:27.305
Why do you insist
on bringing him back to Weiyang?

00:33:27.385 --> 00:33:29.065
That's for later.

00:33:29.145 --> 00:33:31.065
Right now, let's talk
about the helpers thing.

00:33:31.145 --> 00:33:32.985
I'll be honest with you.

00:33:33.505 --> 00:33:36.505
Captain Zhao assigned this case
to me not because of you.

00:33:36.585 --> 00:33:39.305
Everyone thinks it's a prank.
Barely even a case.

00:33:39.385 --> 00:33:40.345
What?

00:33:41.705 --> 00:33:43.705
What kind of logic is that?

00:33:44.225 --> 00:33:46.585
Back when Xu Meng
and her father went missing,

00:33:46.665 --> 00:33:48.105
everyone said it was a prank too.

00:33:48.185 --> 00:33:49.345
Was it?

00:33:54.745 --> 00:33:55.705
Dad,

00:33:57.265 --> 00:33:58.705
stop dwelling on the past.

00:34:00.425 --> 00:34:01.545
Go home.

00:34:02.305 --> 00:34:03.785
I've got work.

00:34:06.145 --> 00:34:06.985
Hey!

00:34:17.625 --> 00:34:24.625
FAIR AND JUST, LOYAL AND TRUE

00:34:32.185 --> 00:34:33.025
Master!

00:34:36.225 --> 00:34:37.865
Master, thank you.

00:34:37.945 --> 00:34:39.705
Master, thank you.

00:34:39.784 --> 00:34:41.905
I really should have
listened to you yesterday

00:34:41.985 --> 00:34:43.025
and gone straight to Yuanlongli.

00:34:43.105 --> 00:34:45.744
Would've saved a lot of trouble.
Thank you so much.

00:34:45.824 --> 00:34:47.225
-Thank you.
-It's nothing.

00:34:47.304 --> 00:34:48.385
No big deal.

00:34:48.465 --> 00:34:49.505
How's your child?

00:34:49.585 --> 00:34:51.545
He is still unconscious.

00:34:51.625 --> 00:34:53.225
The police say he attacked
someone with a knife.

00:34:53.304 --> 00:34:54.385
How is that possible?

00:34:54.465 --> 00:34:57.265
The school wants to expel him.

00:34:57.345 --> 00:35:00.505
I really don't know what to do.

00:35:02.025 --> 00:35:04.145
But he did attack someone.

00:35:04.225 --> 00:35:06.705
Did anyone actually see it?

00:35:06.785 --> 00:35:08.545
Bring that person out
and let them face me.

00:35:08.625 --> 00:35:11.825
I want to see who it was
that knocked him unconscious.

00:35:12.545 --> 00:35:13.745
Master,

00:35:14.825 --> 00:35:15.945
you are experienced.

00:35:16.025 --> 00:35:17.345
Please do a reading for me.

00:35:17.425 --> 00:35:20.225
See whether my child
can get through this safely.

00:35:21.025 --> 00:35:22.305
I don't do fortune-telling.

00:35:22.385 --> 00:35:23.265
I only find people.

00:35:23.905 --> 00:35:25.745
Then please help me find the culprit.

00:35:28.545 --> 00:35:31.825
How about I find you an expert?
If he takes the case,

00:35:31.905 --> 00:35:33.705
your child's situation will definitely
be thoroughly investigated.

00:35:33.785 --> 00:35:34.825
I'll do whatever you say.

00:35:34.905 --> 00:35:36.745
Wait here, I'll call him out.

00:35:37.265 --> 00:35:38.665
Thank you, Master. Thank you.

00:35:41.505 --> 00:35:43.465
He really is remarkable.

00:36:02.065 --> 00:36:04.585
Hurry up. The mother is waiting.

00:36:06.025 --> 00:36:07.145
Move it.

00:36:08.425 --> 00:36:10.105
You're so careless.

00:36:15.625 --> 00:36:17.985
Ms. Wang, I have been looking
for you. Get in the car.

00:36:19.345 --> 00:36:20.865
Officer He, I'm waiting for someone.

00:36:20.945 --> 00:36:23.145
Han Zi'ang's case is now under my charge.

00:36:23.225 --> 00:36:24.705
If you want to find out the truth,
come with me.

00:36:25.865 --> 00:36:28.065
-But…
-Hurry, get in.

00:36:28.705 --> 00:36:30.425
-Alright.
-Kiddo.

00:36:34.985 --> 00:36:36.305
Kiddo.

00:36:51.825 --> 00:36:55.745
Ms. Wang, don't worry too much
about your son's case.

00:36:55.825 --> 00:36:58.625
The victim only has minor injuries.
It's considered a light offense.

00:36:59.225 --> 00:37:00.345
Trust us.

00:37:00.945 --> 00:37:02.345
We'll get to the truth.

00:37:03.785 --> 00:37:07.505
Ang is innocent.

00:37:08.505 --> 00:37:10.185
He's so young.

00:37:10.265 --> 00:37:14.265
If he grows up carrying that,
what will people think of him?

00:37:15.665 --> 00:37:18.065
He's in a private school now.

00:37:19.105 --> 00:37:20.505
Look at me.

00:37:21.105 --> 00:37:25.665
I pulled strings and spent
a lot of money to get him in.

00:37:27.065 --> 00:37:29.585
If he gets expelled,

00:37:31.025 --> 00:37:33.945
our lives will be ruined.

00:37:37.185 --> 00:37:40.585
I'll go to the school tomorrow
and speak to the principal.

00:37:41.905 --> 00:37:44.345
Thank you. Thank you, Officer.

00:37:44.425 --> 00:37:45.705
But I have one condition.

00:37:47.625 --> 00:37:48.745
Go ahead.

00:37:49.985 --> 00:37:51.265
Stop seeing that old man.

00:37:53.225 --> 00:37:54.705
Master?

00:37:54.785 --> 00:37:58.105
-Why?
-He's no master. He's my dad.

00:37:59.665 --> 00:38:01.065
He's a fraud.

00:38:02.065 --> 00:38:03.545
You've got some nerve.

00:38:04.905 --> 00:38:07.105
You tricked Song Qingsong?

00:38:07.705 --> 00:38:11.545
You think someone like him
is that easy to trick?

00:38:12.705 --> 00:38:13.825
He's suspicious.

00:38:15.145 --> 00:38:16.945
Just a few looks
and you call him a suspect?

00:38:17.025 --> 00:38:21.185
Where is the evidence? No evidence,
and now it's backfired on you.

00:38:23.505 --> 00:38:25.865
The traffic police called me.

00:38:25.945 --> 00:38:28.345
They said a Mercedes driver
reported you for rear-ending him.

00:38:28.945 --> 00:38:30.145
He wants 30,000.

00:38:30.825 --> 00:38:31.865
How much?

00:38:32.945 --> 00:38:33.825
Thirty thousand.

00:38:45.745 --> 00:38:47.145
-Done?
-Don't touch it.

00:38:47.225 --> 00:38:48.305
It's not dry yet.

00:38:52.425 --> 00:38:54.025
I'm not letting this go
with Song Qingsong.

00:38:54.105 --> 00:38:55.385
Keep an eye on Xiaohe.

00:38:55.465 --> 00:38:56.625
I'm going to stake out the cement factory.

00:38:56.705 --> 00:38:57.545
He.

00:38:58.865 --> 00:39:00.025
I was impulsive yesterday.

00:39:00.105 --> 00:39:01.345
-I'm afraid…
-Afraid of what?

00:39:01.425 --> 00:39:02.385
I'm not afraid of anyone.

00:39:03.785 --> 00:39:06.465
Dad, is that the bad guy who hit our car?

00:39:06.545 --> 00:39:08.425
I'm going too!

00:39:09.065 --> 00:39:10.065
Kiddo, be good.

00:39:10.145 --> 00:39:13.065
Stay with Uncle Ran today.
I'll pick you up later.

00:39:14.545 --> 00:39:16.705
Don't worry. I am not being impulsive.

00:39:16.785 --> 00:39:18.025
I have to keep an eye on Song Qingsong.

00:39:18.105 --> 00:39:19.825
-If not, he'll slip away.
-He.

00:39:20.545 --> 00:39:24.345
If we can't get him soon,
we'll have no other leads.

00:39:24.905 --> 00:39:27.025
I want to try that maze theory.

00:39:27.105 --> 00:39:29.465
We've only got two days left.
Try whatever theory you've got.

00:39:29.545 --> 00:39:30.585
-I'm heading out.
-Hey!

00:39:31.185 --> 00:39:32.625
Be careful.

00:39:39.945 --> 00:39:42.665
Officer Ran,
this is Luandongzi's statement.

00:39:42.745 --> 00:39:44.585
-We need you to verify it.
-Thank you.

00:39:55.545 --> 00:39:57.585
QUESTION: HOW DID YOU GET IN YUANLONGLI?
ANSWER: YOU'VE CAME TO THE RIGHT PERSON

00:39:58.625 --> 00:40:00.545
There's an underground garage
at Yuanlongli?

00:40:00.625 --> 00:40:01.865
Yes.

00:40:01.945 --> 00:40:03.705
Luandongzi said people who pass by there

00:40:03.785 --> 00:40:05.865
can avoid the cameras at
the security booth and building entrance.

00:40:08.585 --> 00:40:11.145
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

00:40:41.585 --> 00:40:42.745
Officer Ran,

00:40:42.825 --> 00:40:46.625
the entrance to this underground garage
was sealed a few years ago.

00:40:46.705 --> 00:40:50.025
There's only this small access door now.
You need a key.

00:40:50.945 --> 00:40:52.105
Where is the exit?

00:40:53.265 --> 00:40:55.665
Outside the compound. Also needs a key.

00:40:56.265 --> 00:40:58.185
Besides the property management,
who else has keys?

00:40:58.265 --> 00:40:59.425
Not sure.

00:40:59.505 --> 00:41:01.145
You'll have to ask Manager Qian.

00:41:05.505 --> 00:41:08.385
Officer Ran, I need to get back
to the CCTV room.

00:41:08.465 --> 00:41:10.985
I'll leave you here.
All the keys for New York Block are here.

00:41:11.065 --> 00:41:13.345
Return them to the property office
when you're done.

00:41:13.425 --> 00:41:14.745
-Thank you.
-You are welcome.

00:41:14.825 --> 00:41:15.665
I'm heading off.

00:41:15.745 --> 00:41:16.865
-Bye.
-Okay.

00:41:21.585 --> 00:41:22.505
Xiaohe.

00:41:24.785 --> 00:41:27.545
Uncle Ran,
this underground maze is so cool.

00:41:27.625 --> 00:41:29.305
Stay close.

00:41:29.385 --> 00:41:31.265
There might be rats running out.

00:41:31.345 --> 00:41:33.185
I'm not afraid of rats.

00:41:33.265 --> 00:41:36.345
I caught one this big at my grandma's.

00:41:57.665 --> 00:41:58.825
Xiaohe.

00:41:59.545 --> 00:42:00.425
Xiaohe.

00:42:01.585 --> 00:42:04.905
Uncle Ran. I caught a big rat!

00:42:04.985 --> 00:42:07.145
What are you doing? Let go!

00:42:07.785 --> 00:42:08.785
Who are you?

00:42:09.985 --> 00:42:12.025
-Stop shining that light!
-Manager Qian?

00:42:12.105 --> 00:42:12.985
What are you doing here?

00:42:13.625 --> 00:42:16.705
Someone reported
that the motion lights are broken.

00:42:16.785 --> 00:42:17.905
I came to fix them.

00:42:17.985 --> 00:42:18.985
SAFETY FIRST

00:42:21.665 --> 00:42:24.225
Does an electrician's work
need the property manager to handle?

00:42:25.265 --> 00:42:26.225
Oh, come on.

00:42:26.305 --> 00:42:28.185
Uncle Ran, don't believe him.

00:42:28.265 --> 00:42:30.545
He looks more like a thief.

00:42:31.185 --> 00:42:32.545
Watch your mouth.

00:42:32.625 --> 00:42:34.345
Whose daughter are you?

00:42:34.425 --> 00:42:35.745
Officer He's daughter.

00:42:37.105 --> 00:42:38.185
No wonder.

00:42:38.265 --> 00:42:40.385
Your dad and I are good friends.

00:42:40.465 --> 00:42:42.505
You should be calling me Mr. Qian.

00:42:42.585 --> 00:42:45.585
Save it. I'm not friends with a thief.

00:42:45.665 --> 00:42:46.705
You!

00:42:50.945 --> 00:42:52.025
Officer Ran,

00:42:53.345 --> 00:42:55.665
what are you doing down here?

00:43:01.305 --> 00:43:02.825
Stop coughing.

00:43:02.905 --> 00:43:05.385
That penny-pincher
turned off the motion lights.

00:43:05.465 --> 00:43:07.785
-Why?
-To save electricity.

00:43:07.865 --> 00:43:10.425
Tell me, what is he doing
with all that cement?

00:43:10.505 --> 00:43:13.505
-Building a grave at home?
-You two!

00:43:14.905 --> 00:43:15.865
Did you hear that?

00:43:15.945 --> 00:43:17.025
What was that sound?

00:43:17.105 --> 00:43:19.225
Could it be those two missing people?

00:43:19.745 --> 00:43:20.585
Are you serious?

00:43:22.745 --> 00:43:24.265
You two!

00:43:25.705 --> 00:43:27.385
-Oh my goodness!
-Who is it?

00:43:27.465 --> 00:43:29.985
Don't scare me. I'm afraid of the dark!

00:43:35.545 --> 00:43:38.385
You two, get out here now!

00:43:39.545 --> 00:43:40.665
Why aren't you at work?

00:43:40.745 --> 00:43:43.185
What are you doing down here? For what?

00:43:43.265 --> 00:43:44.705
Didn't you tell us to…

00:43:44.785 --> 00:43:45.785
I… Tell…

00:43:45.865 --> 00:43:47.345
Tell what?

00:43:47.425 --> 00:43:48.825
Get back to work!

00:43:53.185 --> 00:43:54.345
Wait.

00:43:57.665 --> 00:43:58.585
You dropped something.

00:44:09.625 --> 00:44:11.585
Officer Ran, I still have things
to do at the property office.

00:44:12.265 --> 00:44:13.785
I'll be heading up now too.

00:44:14.665 --> 00:44:15.705
Hold on.

00:44:19.465 --> 00:44:22.385
Besides the property management,
who else has the key to the garage?

00:44:25.425 --> 00:44:27.905
When Yuanlongli was first built,

00:44:28.425 --> 00:44:29.425
there weren't many cars.

00:44:29.505 --> 00:44:31.185
The vehicle entrance was sealed off.

00:44:31.265 --> 00:44:33.825
At that time,
only the property management had the key.

00:44:33.905 --> 00:44:36.985
But then, later on,
the Pattia Club opened.

00:44:37.065 --> 00:44:38.785
They were afraid of resident complaints,

00:44:38.865 --> 00:44:41.625
so they had their guests
and staff use the garage.

00:44:41.705 --> 00:44:43.705
The keys just couldn't be tracked anymore.

00:44:44.625 --> 00:44:45.505
Officer Ran,

00:44:46.025 --> 00:44:49.945
-I… I'll be going…
-Just go. Mr. Penny-pincher.

00:44:52.825 --> 00:44:54.465
You really take after your dad.

00:45:33.545 --> 00:45:36.985
SAFETY FIRST